<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f4f8fb;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .devboard-email-wrapper {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .devboard-email-container {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            max-width: 420px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 32px;
            padding: 32px 28px 24px 28px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .devboard-title {
            color: #1a2233;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .devboard-text {
            color: #3a465e;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        .devboard-alert {
            background: #fff3f3;
            border: 1px solid #ffd6d6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        .devboard-footer {
            margin-top: 32px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #8a99b3;
        }
        .devboard-footer strong {
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="devboard-email-wrapper">
        <div class="devboard-email-container">
            <div class="devboard-title">Password Changed</div>
            <div class="devboard-text">
                Hello,<br>
                Your <strong>DevBoard</strong> account password has been successfully changed.
            </div>
            <div class="devboard-alert">
                If you did not make this change, please contact our support team immediately.
            </div>
            <div class="devboard-text">
                For security reasons, we recommend that you:
                <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li>Use a strong, unique password</li>
                    <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
                    <li>Regularly update your password</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="devboard-footer">
                This is an automated message, please do not reply.<br>
                &copy; {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} <strong>DevBoard</strong>. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 